Go to the Link :-
https://pub.dev/packages/provider

1)Add the provider depedency in the pubspec.yaml file.Get pub.To verify the process should finish with exit code 0.
2)Create a class that with ChangeNotifier.
  Add getter and setter for that.
  Add notifylistner for the setter
3)Create a Provider with global Context.
4)Create a ChangeProvider Notifier that will accept a provider state.

Important Point:- By Using consumer we can make the Corresponding widget build not the entire Widget tree.
Without Consumer entire widget will be built.


